Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【Main】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.16,0:01:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正直老人號離開了艾斯塔爾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所幸其後沒有被泰坦尼亞發現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}惑星巴格休
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}惑星バルガシュ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順利逃到了巴格休
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.69,0:01:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴格休嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.62,0:01:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先前也來過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴格休地處邊境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:02:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞在此處的勢力應該不強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要躲開泰坦尼亞 這裡最合適不過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.23,0:02:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚會被發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能一味逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能在這裡出現轉機
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 有個人想請提督見見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.01,0:02:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當地反泰坦尼亞勢力的據點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道對方底細
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但主動拜託的話 對方應該會幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就經由其它渠道和此處的流星旗軍聯繫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反泰坦尼亞和流星旗軍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這下應該能熱鬧點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1465,850)\fad(500,500)\fs90\bord4}沙漠之鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗艦隊和正直老人號的交戰記錄到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對此進行分析之後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算出了正直老人號的逃走路線
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的去向是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴格休·卡嘉諾特一帶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞勢力尚未觸及的空域嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來對方的逃走路線也經過一番計算
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.46,0:03:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問如何處置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上向各個星球派遣搜查隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令駐留軍同意搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此失陪 大總統閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一場卓有成果的談判 謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}埃爾伯特·卡納庫大總統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}エルベルト・カナック大統領
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除去泰坦尼亞駐軍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然讓對方同意了全部條件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下官佩服之至
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於駐軍的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一開始就不認為對方會同意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不認同泰坦尼亞統治的星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點也是最招人反感的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 巴格休星也早晚會成為問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你新的赴任地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說哲力胥閣下向巴格休·卡嘉諾特方面派遣了方修利搜查隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥卿果然很著急
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願不會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾密卿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的坐船送你去巴格休吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.35,0:05:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那不是提督先生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來我這邊喝酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有約了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你喜歡那種類型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是沾花惹草的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡喝茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方的聯絡員會帶我們去沙漠裡的藏身之處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然的邂逅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望是場美妙的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.47,0:06:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 已經聯繫上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個座位有人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的是的 不會錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不… 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是長得有一點點像…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 方修利來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是我們的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡等於是反泰坦尼亞的巢穴了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 提督
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 大家好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴格休這樣討厭泰坦尼亞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那些傢伙最近在鎮上到處轉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追 快追
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是幹什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我 你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.06,0:08:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一步吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不用看店了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是聯絡員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然出了點意外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但從那邊可以逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我方特務艦正徹底清查他的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:09:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把巴格休方圓二十里拍上一張衛星照片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現他就只是時間的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們一旦發現 馬上降落到巴格休
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們本隊也向巴格休進發
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這樣會侵害到巴格休的主權…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 告訴巴格休政府
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞的敵人由泰坦尼亞自己抓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若敢妄加干預 小心會後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}塔魯哈利沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}タルハリ砂漠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的首領就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的藏身處還真偏僻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利還真是膽小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是單槍匹馬挑戰泰坦尼亞的男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是對方把我捧起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓對方儘量捧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然豈不是很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不爽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1463,923)\fad(500,500)}伊文·卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1463,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}イブン・カシム
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是伊文·卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.67,0:10:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚好像出了點情況 對不住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 多謝你們救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請恕我單刀直入
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的船上有通訊接進來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去談談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳平安回去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為正直老人號開到了附近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 想請提督暫時留在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是沙漠正中央
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚還是想和你們合流
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞已經來了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時動彈不得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 有情況隨時聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方也想與貴方合作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利提督就交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道反泰坦尼亞派值不值得信任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但朋友還是越多越好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊還順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這個星球上的流星旗軍也不少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該能借我幾艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個萬一的時候就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那張椅子對您來說還是太大了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看來是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 法爾的赴任地好像出了點問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 據說在巴格休星發現了方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真頭痛 看來他還得過幾天才能回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好空氣 活過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒出息 已經喘粗氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個洞窟讓人呼吸困難耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡據說是百萬年前火山熔岩流過來形成的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知深處通往何處
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也從百萬年前就恨著泰坦尼亞 住在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但恨著泰坦尼亞倒是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這種年輕姑娘是為了替父母報仇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.97,0:13:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.54,0:13:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父親是個才華橫溢的鋼琴家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但被和泰坦尼亞有關的競爭對手搶去了機會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:13:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的首領也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時失去了妻兒和醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的人也或多或少和泰坦尼亞有點仇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要和泰坦尼亞作對？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想說的話就當我沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 勉強說來 是為了蛋包飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋包飯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能平安離開這裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就給我做蛋包飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(807,923)\fad(500,500)}泰坦尼亞特務艦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(807,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}タイタニア特務艦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞的特務艦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 在沙漠中央發現生命反應
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下降途中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了方修利的行蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.44,0:15:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的鼠輩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從巢裡鑽出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用等本隊到達
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要抓活的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被泰坦尼亞的特務艦發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願能趕上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也和博士聯絡過了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵力居然如此驚人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須撐到正直老人號趕來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.70,0:17:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這裡不是泰坦尼亞的領土
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們可以隨便動武嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問我也沒用啊 去問哲力胥閣下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷達上有反應了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是巴格休政府保安部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在本地動武屬於違法行為
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是對主權的重大侵害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上解除武裝…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞只服從泰坦尼亞的上級指示
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方不打算撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知地面部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.87,0:18:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一艘小艇果然派不上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.01,0:18:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的槍法有限呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 不開槍就只有死路一條
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:18:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗視裝置是為了捕捉目標
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.33,0:19:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射擊也有所顧慮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.23,0:19:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 對方還不打算殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人知道你是不是方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告各衝要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始投擲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:19:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面部隊的損傷率
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14% 不 達到15%了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不需要生擒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以連洞窟一併破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,損害繼續增大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 這樣下去恐怕會全軍覆沒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了 你真是方修利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 我差點忘了問救命恩人的大名了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}雪拉芬·庫帕斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}セラフィン・クーパーズ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪拉芬·庫帕斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我雪拉就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪拉 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不知道對方的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然還拜託她做蛋包飯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話說得真沒出息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.51,0:21:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若沒出息的方修利能用計打敗他們的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就給你做蛋包飯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一言為定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 是援軍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單憑這艘船行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一對一應該行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在博士趕來之前 我們得撐下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我 提督
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.50,0:22:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴格休星的戰鬥此刻剛剛開始
